00:39:02,072 --> 00:39:12,781
♪

1038
00:39:23,457 --> 00:39:24,524
Hey.

1039
00:39:28,229 --> 00:39:29,763
How're you feeling?

1040
00:39:29,831 --> 00:39:32,032
Better...Now.

1041
00:39:36,770 --> 00:39:39,105
Can I just say something?

1042
00:39:39,173 --> 00:39:40,606
Sure.

1043
00:39:40,674 --> 00:39:42,575
<i>Steve:</i>
<i>The last few months,</i>

1044
00:39:42,642 --> 00:39:46,378
I've been doing a lot
of thinking...

1045
00:39:46,446 --> 00:39:50,149
Just about, uh,
the big picture.

1046
00:39:50,217 --> 00:39:51,550
Yeah. I have too.

1047
00:39:51,618 --> 00:39:53,819
<i>Steve:</i>
<i>Just family...</i>

1048
00:39:53,886 --> 00:39:56,888
Future and stuff.
(Breathes deeply)

1049
00:39:57,957 --> 00:40:02,094
(Clears throat)
And what I'm guessing is...

1050
00:40:04,330 --> 00:40:07,665
Our big pictures
aren't the same.

1051
00:40:09,000 --> 00:40:12,336
'Cause you're in mine,
but, uh...

1052
00:40:15,006 --> 00:40:16,373
I don't think I'm in yours.

1053
00:40:20,946 --> 00:40:23,748
Hey, it's okay.

1054
00:40:26,250 --> 00:40:27,550
It's all good.

1055
00:40:27,618 --> 00:40:29,652
There's no regrets.

1056
00:40:30,587 --> 00:40:33,123
Well...
Almost no regrets.

1057
00:40:34,058 --> 00:40:35,558
What do you mean?

1058
00:40:36,493 --> 00:40:38,194
Never got to finish
our ice cream.

1059
00:40:38,262 --> 00:40:39,629
Both:
(Laugh)

1060
00:40:39,696 --> 00:40:40,763
Ow.

1061
00:40:43,299 --> 00:40:46,201
(Steve inhales
and exhales deeply)

1062
00:40:49,038 --> 00:40:50,605
Just one favour?

1063
00:40:51,540 --> 00:40:53,341
Anything.

1064
00:40:53,409 --> 00:40:55,077
Promise me...

